16:25.218 --> 16:27.186 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: He wanted it.

16:27.220 --> 16:30.256 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: For the
