18:26.939 --> 18:29.842 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Another name,
another very
important name that was
overlooked today.

18:29.875 --> 18:35.381 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Alexander Acosta is the man who
Mr. Trump
would like lead the Labor
Department.

18:35.414 --> 18:36.582 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
