18:36.616 --> 18:37.717 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
He has quite a pedigree.

18:37.750 --> 18:40.619 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
In fact, he has served himself
as a U.S. attorney.

18:40.653 --> 18:46.025 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He also was the first Hispanic
to serve as
an assistant attorney general,
covering civil

18:46.058 --> 18:47.159 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
rights.

18:47.193 --> 18:49.195 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Also, he was on the National
Labor Relations
Board.

18:49.228 --> 18:53.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That in particular is important,
because that's
his main qualification, as far
as we know,

18:53.432 --> 18:55.167 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
for this labor job.

18:55.201 --> 19:00.539 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Currently, he's the dean of the
College of
Law at the Florida International
University.

19:00.573 --> 19:04.143 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He would be first Hispanic on
President Trump's
Cabinet.

19:04.176 --> 19:06.946 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're waiting for reaction from
Capitol Hill
to his name.

19:06.979 --> 19:08.748 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
He is well-known here.

19:08.781 --> 19:11.684 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And one thing the White House
likes, Hari,
in particular, is that he's gone
through the

19:11.717 --> 19:14.587 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
