Senate three
times.

19:14.620 --> 19:17.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now, one of
the things I
want to follow up on is
something that you

19:17.056 --> 19:18.624 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
were asking the president today.

19:18.657 --> 19:20.793 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What's happening, what is the
latest with
the executive order?

19:20.826 --> 19:23.129 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Right, such a
critical piece
of information.

19:23.162 --> 19:28.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The president, as we played for
our audience,
said he will have a new order
out next week.

19:28.768 --> 19:34.540 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It seems that this next order is
an attempt
to almost replicate the past
order, but line

19:34.573 --> 19:38.244 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
