kind of court
muster.

19:38.277 --> 19:43.049 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it also seems, reading
between the lines
-- and I have one source
indicating that they

19:43.082 --> 19:45.384 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
