back-and-forth

20:31.330 --> 20:32.298 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with the press.

20:32.331 --> 20:33.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, it was a lot of that.

20:33.999 --> 20:35.301 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Lisa
