20:35.334 --> 20:37.403 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: You got it.

20:37.436 --> 20:42.408 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now for two
