improv.

21:23.616 --> 21:26.218 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You could see him enjoying
himself.

21:26.252 --> 21:28.587 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think it made him feel better.

21:28.621 --> 21:33.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
