21:36.428 --> 21:39.832 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They are not rattled by anything
they have
seen.

21:39.865 --> 21:44.603 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They're sticking with him, so
they're happy
to sort of see him back out
there being Trump.

21:44.637 --> 21:48.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I thought it was less successful
with the
third audience, which is the
most important.

21:48.707 --> 21:51.610 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
