Most Democrats, polls show, will
never be
for Trump.

21:54.580 --> 21:59.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But there are Trump voters and
others who
are kind of wigglers who I think
would be

21:59.818 --> 22:05.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
