anything
to the reporter or to the
reporters while

22:58.210 --> 22:59.912 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
they're asking us additional
questions.

22:59.945 --> 23:02.281 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He's very confrontational.

23:02.314 --> 23:03.382 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I think that's refreshing.

23:03.415 --> 23:05.184 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I think it actually is going
to be good.

23:05.217 --> 23:08.487 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think the public is going
to take an
interest in these press
conferences much more

23:08.520 --> 23:10.456 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
so than in past presidencies.

23:10.489 --> 23:14.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ruth, it is the
case this president
goes on about the press
virtually every chance

23:14.960 --> 23:15.928 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
he gets.

23:15.961 --> 23:16.929 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We heard that today.

23:16.962 --> 23:18.364 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It took up so much time in his
news conference.

23:18.397 --> 23:21.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You and I know, as somebody --
we have covered
this for a long time.

23:21.600 --> 23:28.474 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Every president feels that he
has gotten unfair,
dishonest coverage from the news
media.

23:28.507 --> 23:32.845 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Is there something
quantitatively, qualitatively
different about the coverage of
this president?

23:32.878 --> 23:36.548 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RUTH MARCUS: Absolutely, both
quantitatively
and qualitatively.

23:36.582 --> 23:40.619 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Other presidents behind the
scenes mutter
epithets about us.

23:40.653 --> 23:45.224 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
