human life
to our face.

23:45.257 --> 23:51.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Other presidents tried their
best to go around
the media that they don't think
are expressing

23:51.096 --> 23:52.931 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
their views.

23:52.965 --> 23:59.038 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump just is -- is
just very, very
vocal about that and much more
-- spends much

23:59.071 --> 24:01.206 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
more time being vocal about
that.

24:01.240 --> 24:07.313 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The question that I have --
certainly, I agree
